Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:10.46,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,First trial in Equestria! No big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:10.46,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,小马国的第一场庭审！不要紧的。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.94,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,The prosecution... is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.94,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,检控方这边准备就绪。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:17.92,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,Nothing was missing from the crime scene to suggest that the murder may have occurred elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:17.92,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,案发现场也没有缺少任何东西，表明命案可能是在其他地方发生的。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:21.68,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,If the crime scene lacks even a drop of blood to speak of,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:21.68,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,如果案发现场连一滴血都看不到，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:25.88,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,that casts significant doubt over whether or not the victim was stabbed there at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:25.88,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,那被害者在这个地方遭捅刺就非常值得怀疑了。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.79,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,My name is Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.79,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,我的名字泽科拉。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:34.15,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,It's entirely possible that our witness, Ms. Zecora, is Royal Order's true killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:34.15,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,我们的证马，泽科拉女士，完全有可能是杀害皇家秩序的真凶！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:37.46,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,you shan't be relying on that theory for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:37.46,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,这个主张你也别指望能坚持多久。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:40.48,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,She's... trying to help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:40.48,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,她…也想帮助他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:45.97,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,then, letting Zecora's testimony stand shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:42.25,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,If she isn't out for blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:45.97,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,那么让泽科拉的证词被采信应该没什么问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:42.25,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,如果她不是冲着对付被告去的，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.97,0:00:50.91,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,You evidently still have much to learn, but punishment from me you have not earned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.97,0:00:50.91,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,律师羽毛未丰满，恳请法官勿为难。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:53.71,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,Are those... pieces of glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:53.71,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,这是…玻璃碎片吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:01.55,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that not a single one of them wears glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:58.40,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,If you run through the profiles of every single pony involved in this case so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:01.55,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,你就会发现他们都不戴眼镜！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:58.40,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,如果你把所有案件相关小马的档案全都翻看一遍的话，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:05.80,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,We know they were there. What matters at this point... is what they saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:05.80,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,我们知道她们去过现场，现在重要的…是她们目击了什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:10.47,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,The defense wishes to call Diamond Tiara and Silver Spoon to the stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:10.47,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,辩护方要求传唤珠玉冠冠和白银勺勺出庭作证！
