Dialogue: 0,2:26:24.28,2:26:27.15,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,You wished to see me, Lord Equity?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:24.28,2:26:27.15,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,您召见我，钧正大人？
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.15,2:26:31.64,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,Yes. Tell me, what's the status of the Manehattan investigation?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.15,2:26:31.64,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,是的。告诉我，马哈顿案的调查进展如何了？
Dialogue: 0,2:26:31.64,2:26:35.63,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,The... Manehattan investigation?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:31.64,2:26:35.63,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,马…马哈顿案的调查？
Dialogue: 0,2:26:35.63,2:26:38.92,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,You were leading it prior to the Ponyville case, were you not?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:35.63,2:26:38.92,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,小马镇案发生之前，那边的调查就是你带的队，没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:26:38.92,2:26:41.87,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know if there were any new developments.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:38.92,2:26:41.87,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,我想知道现在进展如何。
Dialogue: 0,2:26:41.87,2:26:44.53,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,N-Not that I know of...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:41.87,2:26:44.53,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,据、据我所知还没有...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:44.53,2:26:48.90,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,I haven't had a chance to return to the city since Royal Order's murder.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:44.53,2:26:48.90,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,自从皇家秩序被害后，我一直没机会回去。
Dialogue: 0,2:26:48.90,2:26:53.35,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,And... with how things are over there at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,2:26:48.90,2:26:53.35,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,而且...考虑到那边的情况，
Dialogue: 0,2:26:53.35,2:26:56.87,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid the investigation's been at a deadlock.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:53.35,2:26:56.87,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,恐怕调查陷入了僵局。
Dialogue: 0,2:27:00.30,2:27:03.33,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,I have good news about Royal Order's murder, though.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:00.30,2:27:03.33,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,不过关于皇家秩序的谋杀案我有好消息汇报。
Dialogue: 0,2:27:03.33,2:27:07.85,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,There's been a breakthrough in the case. Once I get back to Ponyville, I—
Dialogue: 0,2:27:03.33,2:27:07.85,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,案子有了突破。一旦我回到小马镇，我——
Dialogue: 0,2:27:08.39,2:27:12.17,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,The Manehattan investigation MUST continue, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:08.39,2:27:12.17,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,马哈顿案的调查{\fs90}必须{\fs}继续，刑警。
Dialogue: 0,2:27:12.17,2:27:14.61,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,It cannot be put off any longer.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:12.17,2:27:14.61,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,不能再拖下去了。
Dialogue: 0,2:27:14.61,2:27:19.24,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,You either return to Manehattan, and resume your duties there as lead detective,
Dialogue: 0,2:27:14.61,2:27:19.24,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,要么，你回马哈顿，继续担任调查组长。
Dialogue: 0,2:27:19.24,2:27:23.18,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,or forfeit authority over that case to somepony else.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:19.24,2:27:23.18,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,要么，你就把案子移交给别马处理。
Dialogue: 0,2:27:23.18,2:27:25.24,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,Do I make myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:23.18,2:27:25.24,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,我说得够清楚了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.24,2:27:29.21,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, Lord Equity. I understand. But...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.24,2:27:29.21,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,是、是的，钧正大人，我明白，但...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:31.02,2:27:35.07,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,You desire to continue the investigation into Royal's death, then.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:31.02,2:27:35.07,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,看来，你是想继续调查秩序的案件。
Dialogue: 0,2:27:35.10,2:27:37.72,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,... I do, yes
Dialogue: 0,2:27:35.10,2:27:37.72,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,…如您所说。
Dialogue: 0,2:27:37.72,2:27:43.62,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,Very well. I will assign another investigator to take over the Manehattan investigation.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:37.72,2:27:43.62,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,那好，我会指派另一位调查员接管马哈顿案的调查。
Dialogue: 0,2:27:43.62,2:27:47.91,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,O-Of course. Thank you for your compassion, Lord Equity.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:43.62,2:27:47.91,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,当、当然，感谢你的宽宏大量，钧正大人。
Dialogue: 0,2:27:47.91,2:27:49.86,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,Is that all you wished to see me for?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:47.91,2:27:49.86,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,请问还有别的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:27:49.86,2:27:55.19,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,Yes. You may go, but do not return to Ponyville just yet, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:49.86,2:27:55.19,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,没有。你可以走了，但先别回小马镇，刑警。
Dialogue: 0,2:27:55.19,2:27:57.25,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why not?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:55.19,2:27:57.25,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,为、为什么？
Dialogue: 0,2:27:57.25,2:28:01.69,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,As soon as I've finished re-assigning the case, I will be accompanying you there.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:57.25,2:28:01.69,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,等我把案子重新分配好后，我跟你一起过去。
Dialogue: 0,2:28:01.69,2:28:02.61,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:01.69,2:28:02.61,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,您要去？
Dialogue: 0,2:28:03.61,2:28:06.23,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,What for, if I may ask?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:03.61,2:28:06.23,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,为什么，能告诉我吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:28:06.23,2:28:08.77,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,That is none of your concern, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:06.23,2:28:08.77,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,这就不劳你上心了，刑警。
Dialogue: 0,2:28:08.77,2:28:12.10,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,Ah, my apologies, Lord Equity.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:08.77,2:28:12.10,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,啊，我很抱歉，钧正大人。
Dialogue: 0,2:28:12.72,2:28:14.63,White-底部居中-英文,,0,0,0,,I'll await your call, then.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:12.72,2:28:14.63,White-底部居中,,0,0,0,,我等您消息。
